(155, 3, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p> </p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', sans-serif;"> </span></p> <p class="MsoNormal">Dear Somatic Experiencing® and Polarity® Community.</p> <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>I am happy, beyond words, to a <script src="plugins/editors/tinymce/jscripts/tiny_mce/themes/advanced/langs/en.js" type="text/javascript"></script> nnounce to all of you that we are finally opening our healing center in the Ocean and Jungles of Brazil.</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p>  <!--more-->  <p> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">The name of our first retreat is:</p> <p class="MsoNormal">The Healing Journey: Beyond Self Care</p> <p class="MsoNormal">--A Dynamic, Ecological Adventure and Exploration of Mind, Body and Spirit</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">Following the primitive indigenous spirit of authenticity and simplicity,</p> <p class="MsoNormal">We have chosen the magical region near Itacaré Brazil as a backdrop for changing reference, culture, and the very special spirituality and shamanism unique to Brazil.</p> <p class="MsoNormal">We will be taking a small group and invite you to participate in our maiden journey starting on April 15th to April 24th 2010.  This coming week we will be posting photographs and information about the event.  Our new website is: www.brazilhealingcenter.com or www.somaticexperiencing.com  Our email is: traumahealing@gmail.com</p> <p class="MsoNormal">You can also go to “Google earth” and enter: Itacare, Bahia, Brazil.  The retreat center, Sabia Pedra is about 12 Km into the jungle, along the river, from its mouth in Itacaré.  You can click on the little squares on Google to see several photographs that people have taken of the area.</p> <p class="MsoNormal">Please visit us at our website next week and then consider joining us for ten days of this magical encounter.</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">Até logo (Until then),</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">Peter A Levine</p> <p> </p> <p> </p>', 'The Brasil Healing Journey has begun', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-brasil-healing-journey-has-begun', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/?p=155', 2, 'post', '', 0),
(156, 3, '2010-03-19 23:48:39', '2010-03-19 23:48:39', '<h5><span style="font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px;">We have been busy here at Somaticexperiencing.com, completely rebuilding the website on a<a href="http://www.joomla.org" target="_blank" title="Get Joomla!"> Joomla!-</a> Based CMS platform. If you don\'t know what any of this means, don\'t worry. It just gives me added functionality and flexibility to better serve the somaticexperiencing.com audience, as well to better accomplish our primary mission, which is to provide people with resources they need to prevent and heal trauma.</span></h5> <p>Please go to our<a href="http://localhost:8888/speed/2009/09/23/welcome-to-somaticexperiencingcom-natures-lessons-in-healing-trauma/" target="_blank" title="Email page"> Email page</a> to send feedback.</p>', 'A New Site is Here!', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-new-site-design', '', '', '2014-09-29 11:29:47', '2014-09-29 18:29:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/2010/03/19/the-new-site-design/', 1, 'post', '', 0),
