(177, 3, '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p>Dr. Levine has been awarded the lifetime achievement award from the <a target="_blank" title="USABP Homepage" href="http://usabp.org/displaycommon.cfm?an=3">United States Association for Body Psychotherapy</a> (USABP), at their annual conference October 22nd through the 24th at John F. Kennedy University in Pleasant Hills, Ca. &nbsp;</p> <p>Peter is thrilled to receive such an honor, and&nbsp;will be giving the Keynote address on October 23rd, as well as teaching a post-conference workshop and will be serving on the Conference panel in the afternoon.</p> <p><img class=" size-full wp-image-176" style="background-color: #eeeeee; display: block; padding: 4px;" alt="USABP-conference" height="85" width="300" src="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/USABP-conference1.jpg" width="564" height="160" /></p> <p>For more information, or to <a target="_blank" title="Enroll NOW!" href="http://www.usabp.org/displayconvregister.cfm?convnbr=7093">enroll</a>, please check out the USABP Conference <a target="_blank" title="USABP Conference Page" href="http://usabp.org/displayconvention.cfm?conventionnbr=7093">Homepage</a>.&nbsp;</p>', 'Dr. Levine Receives a Lifetime Achievement Award From USABP!', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'dr-levine-receives-a-lifetime-achievement-award-from-usabp', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/?p=177', 17, 'post', '', 0),
