(193, 3, '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Case_consult.jpg" title="Full Size"><img class=" size-full wp-image-190" src="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Case_consult.jpg" width="200" height="200" alt="Case_consult" width="612" height="612" /></a></p> <p>The SE® Trauma Institute is privileged to offer a day of case consultations and demonstrations with author and founder of the Somatic Experiencing® trauma resolution model, Peter A. Levine, PhD.&nbsp;</p> <p>Open to Therapists using body focused approaches, body workers, chiropractors, acupuncturists, nurses, etc. and open to training participants and practitioners of Somatic Experiencing®. The Day is geared for Intermediate students or above, however, Beginners are welcome to present a case or ask questions. Each three hours of consultation time equals one hour credit toward the required eighteen hours for SEP certification. <strong>Remember to bring your session log to receive SEP credit.&nbsp;</strong></p> <blockquote> <p><em>"This is an ideal opportunity to observe Peter modeling his highly creative, intelligent and sensitve healing skills in an intimate and comfortable environment. His demonstrations and explantions furthered my understanding of the myriad of compleixties and simplicities of Somatic Experiencing®. This last supervision with Peter was unforgettable, profound, inspiring and a very encouraging experience for me as a practitioner." </em>Victoria Mihich, MA, MFT, SEP</p> <p> </p> <p>Please contact Joan Luly for <a href="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/caseconsultflyer1.pdf" target="_blank">more information</a>: joansehealing@mac.com. Also, view our PDF\'s for <a href="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/registration_form.pdf" target="_blank">sign up forms</a> and information about submitting as a demo client.&nbsp;</p> </blockquote>', 'See Peter Work in San Diego, November 5th', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'see-peter-work-in-san-diego-november-5th', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/?p=193', 14, 'post', '', 0),
