(197, 3, '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '<p>Presented by the <a href="http://www.themeadows.com/" title="The Meadows Homepage" target="_blank">Meadows Addiction Treatment Center</a></p> <p><img class=" size-full wp-image-196" src="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/meadows-logo.png" width="341" height="138" alt="meadows-logo" width="341" height="138" /></p> <p>The Meadows Addiction and PTSD treatment center (for whom Dr. Levine is a consultant) will be hosting Peter at various events around the country, wherein he will speak about the nature of trauma, how it is a condition that can be healed from, as well as how the body is utilized to make that happen. More information will be found at the Meadows <a target="_blank" title="Sign up here" href="http://www.themeadows.com/events/event/in-an-unspoken-voice-how-the-body-releases-trauma-and-restores-goodness/">website</a> once details have been formalized. However, Peter has agreed to these dates:</p> <p> </p> <ul> <li>March 1st - Los Angeles California - Skirball Cultural Center. </li> <li>9:00am to 12:00pm</li> <li></li> </ul> <ul> <li>March 30th - Milbrae California - Westin San Francisco&nbsp;</li> <li>12:00pm to 4:00pm</li> </ul> <p> </p> <p>CEU\'s are available.&nbsp;</p> <p>You can contact The Meadows through their <a target="_parent" title="Email The Meadows" href="http://www.themeadows.org/contact.html">webmail</a> form for more info.</p>', 'Dr. Levine will present In An Unspoken Voice this March', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', 'dr-levine-will-present-in-an-unspoken-voice-this-march', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/?p=197', 11, 'post', '', 0),
