(369, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '<h2>Instructions:</h2> <p>On this page are two videos that are guided demonstrations of SE®, "Ray - Iraqi War Vet" and "Baby Jack." There are two copies of each. A <a href="#direct">direct download version</a> and a <a href="#flash">flash player version</a>:</p> <p>For your convenience and highest quality, I have links to download these files directly to your computer. Right-Click on the two links below and choose "Save Target As..." or "Save Link As..." (depending on your system). Then tell the computer where and what-name you want it saved as. I would recommend saving to the desktop. Then wait a while for it to download. Once it\'s done, find where you saved your file and then play it. It should be compatible with most media players out there.</p> <p>If this doesn\'t work for you, then please use the flash player versions below. they are both in flash video format, and can be played inside the browser.&nbsp;</p> <h2><a name="direct"></a>Direct Download (Right click and "Save Link As...")</h2> <ul> <li> <h3><a target="_blank" href="images/stories/video/uk_pbr_se_vids/se_militaryrev6.6small.mp4">Ray - Iraqi War Vet</a>&nbsp;(131MB)</h3> </li> <li> <h3><a target="_blank" href="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/baby_jack-final1.mp4">Baby Jack</a>&nbsp;(93.4 MB)</h3> </li> </ul> <p>&nbsp;</p> <h2><a name="flash"></a>Flash player versions&nbsp;</h2> <h3>Ray - Iraqi War Vet -&nbsp;</h3> <p>{flowplayer size=720x405 img=http://somaticexperiencing.com/Video/preview/se_military.jpg}images/stories/video/uk_pbr_se_vids/se_militaryrev6.6small.mp4{/flowplayer}</p> <p>*please be patient as it downloads.&nbsp;</p> <h3>Baby Jack -</h3> <p>{flowplayer size=720x480 img=http://somaticexperiencing.com/Video/preview/baby_jack.jpg}images/stories/video/uk_pbr_se_vids/baby_jack-final.mp4{/flowplayer}</p>', 'Somatic Experiencing©: A therapeutic approach to the needs of Iraq and Afghani Soldiers & Baby Jack', '', 'i