(370, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '</p><img class=" size-full wp-image-181" src="http://localhost:8888/speed/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/ale_duarte1.jpeg" alt="" width="640" height="380" /> <p>Our good friend Ale Duarte, who\'s truly inspirational work leading trauma disaster teams after the Thailand Tsunami, Hurricane Katrina, Sichuan Province, and now in Japan, was recognized and profiled by Japanese News Service NHK <span style="font-size: 8pt;"><sub><a target="_blank" href="http://www3.nhk.or.jp/nhkworld/english/movie/feature201105250915.html">(Permalink)</a>.&nbsp;</sub></span></p> <p>Ale is a gifted SE practitioner, and one of the most amazing people ever. Please watch.&nbsp;</p>  <p>{bo_videojs width=[640] height=[380] autoplay=[false] loop=[false] video_mp4=[images/stories/video/ale_nhk/ale_duarte.mp4]  image=["images/stories/video/ale_nhk/ale_duarte.jpeg"]}   Courtesy of NHK.', 'Ale Duarte on NHK!', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '182-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '2014-05-22 02:31:09', '', 182, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/182-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
