(386, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p> </p> <p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: \'Trebuchet MS\', sans-serif;"> </span></p> <p class="MsoNormal">Dear Somatic Experiencing® and Polarity® Community.</p> <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="white-space: pre;"> </span>I am happy, beyond words, to a <script src="plugins/editors/tinymce/jscripts/tiny_mce/themes/advanced/langs/en.js" type="text/javascript"></script> nnounce to all of you that we are finally opening our healing center in the Ocean and Jungles of Brazil.</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p>  <!--more-->  <p> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">The name of our first retreat is:</p> <p class="MsoNormal">The Healing Journey: Beyond Self Care</p> <p class="MsoNormal">--A Dynamic, Ecological Adventure and Exploration of Mind, Body and Spirit</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">Following the primitive indigenous spirit of authenticity and simplicity,</p> <p class="MsoNormal">We have chosen the magical region near Itacaré Brazil as a backdrop for changing reference, culture, and the very special spirituality and shamanism unique to Brazil.</p> <p class="MsoNormal">We will be taking a small group and invite you to participate in our maiden journey starting on April 15th to April 24th 2010.  This coming week we will be posting photographs and information about the event.  Our new website is: www.brazilhealingcenter.com or www.somaticexperiencing.com  Our email is: traumahealing@gmail.com</p> <p class="MsoNormal">You can also go to “Google earth” and enter: Itacare, Bahia, Brazil.  The retreat center, Sabia Pedra is about 12 Km into the jungle, along the river, from its mouth in Itacaré.  You can click on the little squares on Google to see several photographs that people have taken of the area.</p> <p class="MsoNormal">Please visit us at our website next week and then consider joining us for ten days of this magical encounter.</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">Até logo (Until then),</p> <p class="MsoNormal"> </p> <p class="MsoNormal">Peter A Levine</p> <p> </p> <p> </p>', 'The Brasil Healing Journey has begun', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '155-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 155, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/155-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(387, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p>http://www.trauma-pages.com</p> <p> </p> <p>Forgot who this is.</p> <p> </p> <p> </p>', 'David Baldwin', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '151-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 151, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/151-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(388, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p>http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;q=damasio-a&amp;btnG=Search</p> <p>This paper (available free through google scholar) is about the rebuke of Descartes\' duality of mind and body, and that there is only one, bodymind.</p>', 'Antonio Damasio', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '150-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 150, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/150-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(389, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p>http://drdansiegel.com</p> <p> </p> <p>Dr. Siegel is a premier mind-body specialist. Check out some of his books, which are bestsellers, <em>The Mindful Brain</em>.</p>', 'Dan Siegel', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '149-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 149, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/149-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(390, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p>http://www.stephenporges.info</p> <p> </p> <p>Dr. Porges has written one of the most important papers describing and justifying the case for bottom-up processing known as the Polyvagal Theory of Emotion.</p>', 'Stephen Porges, Ph.D.', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '148-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 148, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/148-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(391, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p><br />Bessel and Peter do a workshop in <a href="http://www.esalen.org" target="_blank" title="www.esalen.org">Esalen</a> in Big Sur, California every spring. Bessel has discovered the link between</p> <p><a href="http://www.traumacenter.org" target="_blank" title="Trauma Researcher Bessel van der Kolk">http://www.traumacenter.org</a></p> <p> </p>', 'Bessel van der Kolk and the Trauma Center', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '147-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 147, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/147-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(392, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p>Everyone has questions about trauma, what it is, and how to get help. Unfortunately, Peter can\'t guide everyone. It is unethical for him to give case consultations or advice to anyone that he is not directly related to. If you are looking for help with a trauma issue, we recommend that you find a Somatic Experiencing Practitioner (SEP) in your area, please see the <a href="http://www.traumahealing.com/somatic-experiencing/practitioner-directory.html" target="_blank" title="Find a Practitioner">Practitioners Registry</a> at the traumahealing website for the Foundation for Human Enrichment, a non-profit organization started by Peter, to oversee the training of therapists in his techniques. <br /><br /></p>', 'I have a question about trauma, can you help?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '145-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 145, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/145-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(393, 1, '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '<p>Unfortunately, due to his current time constraints, he is unable to see private clients. However, he has 5,000 people training in Somatic Experiencing globally, and the best way is to check out the <a href="http://www.traumahealing.com/somatic-experiencing/practitioner-directory.html" target="_blank" title="Find a Practitioner">Practitioners Registry</a> There are still chances to see him by checking out his events page.</p>', 'Does Peter see private clients?', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '144-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '2014-05-22 02:31:30', '', 144, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/144-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
