(474, 3, '2014-08-07 15:18:42', '2014-08-07 22:18:42', 'Somatic Experiencing® is an art form as much as a technique. Sessions are catered to the needs of the client at that particular time. However, you can expect to sit with your therapist, who will begin by asking you talk about a recent period of your day, and as you relate the details of the episode, your therapist will draw your awareness to your unconscious body gestures, and encourage you to explore the sensations that appear while discussing', 'What is a SE® session like?', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2014-09-17 12:41:57', '2014-09-17 19:41:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/?post_type=features&#038;p=474', 5, 'features', '', 0),
