(479, 3, '2014-08-11 14:44:21', '2014-08-11 21:44:21', 'In Somatic Experiencing®, the traumatic event isn\'t what caused the trauma, it is the overwhelmed response to the perceived life threat that is causing an unbalanced nervous system. Our aim is to help you access the <em>body memory</em> of the event, not the story. So we don\'t discuss what happens if you don\'t want to.', 'Don\'t Re-live. Renegotiate.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dont-talk-about-the-event', '', '', '2014-09-17 12:38:21', '2014-09-17 19:38:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/speed/?post_type=features&#038;p=479', 2, 'features', '', 0),
